Paper: hep-th/0007028

Date: 2000-07-04

Title: Holography in an Early Universe with Asymmetric Inflation

Authors: Elcio Abdalla and L. Alejandro Correa-Borbonet

Comments: The correct discussion of the holography problem in the Einstein

frame has replaced a previous oneJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B489 (2000) 383-389

We discuss the validity of the holographic principle in a $(4+n)$ dimensionaluniverse in an asymmetric inflationary phase.